  "dct:provenance": "Curated from primary papers, official repositories, model hubs, project pages, and explicit licence or access terms. All 377 candidates received source-level review on 2026-07-13 against the recorded source baseline. The 345 records meeting the release policy form the canonical displayed catalog; 32 unresolved candidates are preserved losslessly in a separate under-review register. Generated distributions come from the canonical JSON through a deterministic build.",
